    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What is Sage Labs Starbased?" class="article-title">
          What is Sage Labs Starbased?
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:23:34Z" title="2025-12-08T18:23:34Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:23</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47061430667027-What-is-Sage-Labs-Starbased/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener"><strong>SAGE Labs</strong></a> is Star Atlas’ <strong>browser-based 4X strategy game</strong>, built entirely on the <strong>Solana blockchain</strong>. It’s a <strong>play-to-earn experience</strong> where every action, exploring, mining, crafting, and transporting, is signed and settled on-chain.</p><p>Unlike traditional games, <a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener">SAGE Labs</a> features an <strong>on-chain economy</strong> where players can earn <a href="https://support.staratlas.com/star-atlas-tokens" rel="noopener"><strong>ATLAS</strong></a>, the native in-game currency. <a href="https://support.staratlas.com/star-atlas-tokens" rel="noopener">ATLAS</a> is a <strong>crypto token</strong> that:</p><ul>
<li><p>Can be used to buy ships, crew, and resources in the <a href="https://play.staratlas.com/market/?symbol=ATLAS" rel="noopener">Star Atlas Marketplace</a></p></li>
<li><p>Can be traded directly on the <strong>Solana blockchain</strong> using decentralized exchanges (DEXs), such as <a href="https://jup.ag/" rel="noopener">Jupiter</a> or <a href="https://raydium.io/swap/" rel="noopener">Raydium</a></p></li>
</ul><p>Everything you collect or produce, ships, resources, crafted components, exists as <strong>digital assets</strong> in your wallet, giving you full ownership and compatibility across the Star Atlas ecosystem.</p><h3 id="h_01KBJR6AG2HQAF7ZYSNYW763KK">Key Features of SAGE Labs:</h3><ul>
<li><p><strong>On-chain Gameplay</strong>: Every move, mine, or craft is a blockchain transaction.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Fleet Management</strong>: Import ships, crew, and resources to form strategic fleets.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Exploration &amp; Resource Mining</strong>: Discover valuable materials across the Galia Expanse.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Crafting &amp; Transport</strong>: Build refined goods and deliver them between starbases.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Earn ATLAS</strong><br>There are multiple ways to earn ATLAS while playing:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Sell mined or crafted <strong>resources</strong> to other players</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Craft items</strong> and components, then sell them on the open market</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Rent your fleet</strong> to others using Fleet Rental</p></li>
<li><p>Contribute resources to <strong>Starbase upkeep</strong> and earn <strong>Loyalty Points (LP)</strong>, redeemable for ATLAS</p></li>
<li><p>Craft and sell <strong>Faction Infrastructure Contracts (FICs)</strong> for guaranteed ATLAS buyback at select starbases</p></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul><h3 id="h_01KBJR6AG210RTW3F26AY7M5PW">To Get Started, You’ll Need:</h3><ul>
<li><p>A <strong>Solana wallet</strong> (like <a href="https://phantom.com/download" rel="noopener">Phantom</a>)</p></li>
<li><p>Some <strong>SOL</strong> for transactions</p></li>
<li><p><strong>ATLAS</strong> to buy ships, crew, and R4 resources (Fuel, Food, Ammo, Toolkits)</p></li>
</ul><p>🔗 Learn more in our full <a href="https://atmta.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/47053533098387" target="_new" rel="noopener"><strong>SAGE Labs Support Category</strong></a></p></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

